{"author":{"id":"daecaa79b752289d08fa06c7a65c8d0387caf00b7e262b5741f4805727d0a582"},"ops":[{"type":6,"timestamp":1722566078,"nonce":"1r9FxpRigOCXFt2sDq/SQH0elYc=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lAHOCGKeh86RqnmzzmE2BgQ"},"target":"de40b68625bc869c466d372935822027e61421067938377627a2341301e01d39","message":"For simpler launching of both the web and terminal UI components, and to support better domain grouping, we should support a unified command syntax for launching the UIs.\n\n## Example commands\n\nLaunch the web UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui web [--port PORT]\n```\n\nLaunch the TUI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui terminal\n```\n\nStore a preferred default UI (e.g. in git configuration)\n\n```\ngit bug ui set-default terminal\n```\n\nLaunch the configured default UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui\n```","files":null},{"type":6,"timestamp":1722566382,"nonce":"xqaVDxDushFhYyMIHgSEj005AQo=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lAHOCGKeh86RqnmzzmE2FK4"},"target":"de40b68625bc869c466d372935822027e61421067938377627a2341301e01d39","message":"For simpler launching of both the web and terminal UI components, and to support better domain grouping, we should support a unified command syntax for launching the UIs.\n\n## Example commands\n\nLaunch the web UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui web [options]\n```\n\nLaunch the TUI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui terminal\n```\n\nStore a preferred default UI (e.g. in git configuration)\n\n```\ngit bug ui set-default terminal\n```\n\nLaunch the configured default UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui\n```\n\n## Historical commands\n\nThe historical commands should emit a deprecation notice and be removed in the next major release after this feature is merged (semver syntax: `MAJOR . MINOR . PATCH`).\n\nThese are:\n\n- git bug termui\n- git bug webui","files":null},{"type":6,"timestamp":1722566426,"nonce":"qOOU8BHKjvHrEa5MxgJgdP2izco=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lAHOCGKeh86RqnmzzmE2FpA"},"target":"de40b68625bc869c466d372935822027e61421067938377627a2341301e01d39","message":"For simpler launching of both the web and terminal UI components, and to support better domain grouping, we should support a unified command syntax for launching the UIs.\n\n## Example commands\n\nLaunch the web UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui web [options]\n```\n\nLaunch the TUI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui terminal\n```\n\nStore a preferred default UI (e.g. in git configuration)\n\n```\ngit bug ui set-default terminal\n```\n\nLaunch the configured default UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui\n```\n\n## Historical commands\n\nThe historical commands should emit a deprecation notice and be removed in the next major release after this feature is merged (semver syntax: `MAJOR . MINOR . PATCH`).\n\nThese are:\n\n- `git bug termui`\n- `git bug webui`","files":null},{"type":6,"timestamp":1722566485,"nonce":"cNEiZ4+cjWCWgsVGMJGRl3L91Z8=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lAHOCGKeh86RqnmzzmE2GYY"},"target":"de40b68625bc869c466d372935822027e61421067938377627a2341301e01d39","message":"For simpler launching of both the web and terminal UI components, and to support better domain grouping, we should support a unified command syntax for launching the UIs.\n\n## Example commands\n\nLaunch the web UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui web [options]\n```\n\nLaunch the TUI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui terminal\n```\n\nStore a preferred default UI (e.g. in git configuration)\n\n```\n$ git bug ui set-default terminal\n$ git bug ui set-default web [options]\n```\n\nLaunch the configured default UI:\n\n```\ngit bug ui\n```\n\n## Historical commands\n\nThe historical commands should emit a deprecation notice and be removed in the next major release after this feature is merged (semver syntax: `MAJOR . MINOR . PATCH`).\n\nThese are:\n\n- `git bug termui`\n- `git bug webui`","files":null},{"type":5,"timestamp":1722565960,"nonce":"euII/W5lfnRyadTW3hz7LJNuBxM=","metadata":{"github-id":"LE_lADOCGKeh86RqnmzzwAAAAMyqOcr"},"added":["kind/feature"],"removed":[]},{"type":5,"timestamp":1722565960,"nonce":"Pr2ydrKOIVPr46cQdkdRxlSW5os=","metadata":{"github-id":"LE_lADOCGKeh86RqnmzzwAAAAMyqOcx"},"ad